long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically redirects to any zoom link that exists within a URL.

This was created to resolve an issue where Google Calendar event locations contains both a physical location (eg a conference room) and a Zoom link. Current behavior opens a Google Maps link that has an embedded zoom link inside it.

With this extensions - clicking on any link that also contains a Zoom URL will automatically redirect to the zoom address.
